title: AMD_Catalyst_Preview_driver_OpenGL_4.2_beta_support_WinXP.exe
description:
here we are

this an update version of previous catalyst 11.8 from July but this time AMD brings full support for the new openGL 4.2 beta version now.
This the very newest Catalyst 11.8 OGL 4.2 beta preview August 10
file is called :
AMD_Catalyst_Preview_driver_OpenGL_4.2_beta_support_XP
and has been released to public on August 10
official release anyway.
this driver doesn't get full WHQL yet from MS lab but however
is AMD signed anyway.
